name: Detroit City MI City Ward 1
sameAsNote: The current city charter for Detroit uses the terms district and ward interchangeably to describe the drawn political units for which members of the city council, board of police, and community advisory councils are elected (2-105.A.12 & 3-108). While these terms are interchangeable, all of the aforementioned bodies refer to their political geographies as "districts" on their respective websites, so the 'council_district' type should be the preferred identifier.
